<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word" xml:lang="ko"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" leadingSilence="0"><translations><translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="en-US"><text for="L61">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L60">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L63">It's alright</text><text for="L62">It's alright <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(It's alright)</span></text><text for="L21">Two fools who love each other to death</text><text for="L65">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L20">Yeah, we're psycho, psycho</text><text for="L64">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L23">I lose all my energy</text><text for="L67">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L22">Without you, I feel dizzy, I feel empty</text><text for="L66">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L25">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L69">It's alright</text><text for="L24">They say we're meant to be</text><text for="L68">It's alright</text><text for="L27">I'm original visual</text><text for="L26">Hey, trouble, you crash in without a warning</text><text for="L29">It's not scary <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(I just find it interesting)</span></text><text for="L28">We were always like this, yeah</text><text for="L70">We're slightly twisted</text><text for="L71">Psycho</text><text for="L30">It's hot! Let me just hop</text><text for="L32">You make me struggle, I'm trying to soothe you</text><text for="L31">How do I handle you? <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Ooh, ooh-ooh)</span></text><text for="L34">But sometimes, you smile at me</text><text for="L33">I kick you hard as well</text><text for="L36">Our relationship is beautifully tragic</text><text for="L35">How could I ever let you go? Ooh-ooh</text><text for="L38">Like the moon and the river, we hold on tight all over again</text><text for="L37">We make each other shine <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Tell me now)</span></text><text for="L39">You got me feeling like a psycho, psycho</text><text for="L41">We fight like we'll never speak again, then stick together like glue</text><text for="L40">People look at us and say again and again</text><text for="L43">Yeah, we're psycho, psycho <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Yeah, we're psycho, psycho)</span></text><text for="L42">They don't get it, they think it's crazy</text><text for="L45">Without you, I feel dizzy, I feel empty</text><text for="L44">Two fools who love each other to death <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Fools, fools)</span></text><text for="L47">They say we're meant to be</text><text for="L46">I lose all my energy</text><text for="L49">Don't look back</text><text for="L48">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L1">Psycho</text><text for="L2">What am I supposed to do with you?</text><text for="L50">Let's just do things our way</text><text for="L3">I've never felt this way before</text><text for="L4">Up and down, it's a rollercoaster</text><text for="L52">Everything will be OK</text><text for="L5">And I can't seem to get a grip</text><text for="L51">I feel you in every inch of me</text><text for="L6">But one thing's for sure</text><text for="L10">And you know it all too well</text><text for="L54">People look at us and say again and again</text><text for="L7">I don't play the game</text><text for="L53"><span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(You got me feeling like)</span> Like a psycho, psycho</text><text for="L8">They say we're strange</text><text for="L12">But I do the same to you</text><text for="L56">They say we're meant to be</text><text for="L9">But I just love you too much</text><text for="L11">You twist me around your fingers</text><text for="L55">We fight like we'll never speak again, then stick together like glue</text><text for="L14">Breaking each other apart <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Each other apart)</span></text><text for="L58">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L13">We're an odd, twisted kind of love</text><text for="L57">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L16">You got me feeling like a psycho, psycho</text><text for="L15">Only to hold each other close again <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Only to hold each other close again)</span></text><text for="L59">Hey now, we'll be ok</text><text for="L18">We fight like we'll never speak again, then stick together like glue</text><text for="L17">People look at us and say again and again</text><text for="L19">They don't get it, they think it's crazy</text></translation></translations><songwriters><songwriter>Andrew Scott</songwriter><songwriter>Cazzi Opeia</songwriter><songwriter>EJAE</songwriter><songwriter>Kenzie</songwriter></songwriters><transliterations><transliteration automaticallyCreated="true" xml:lang="ko-Latn"><text for="L61"><span begin="3:03.917" end="3:04.205" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">Hey</span> <span begin="3:04.205" end="3:04.384" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">now,</span> <span begin="3:04.460" end="3:04.579" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">we'll</span> <span begin="3:04.579" end="3:04.742" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">be</span> <span begin="3:04.742" end="3:05.054" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ok</span></text><text for="L60"><span begin="3:02.176" end="3:02.464" xmlns="